	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=83141><span id=Scholar>Ellon the Charming</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>37 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.25]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Fel, thank you for your clarification.&nbsp;&nbsp;I recently found out about that too.<br><br>Hence, this weapon is really a 44/48, but has a chance of having 4 points of damage resisted.<br><br>Still, unless the mob was 100% MR, you could still say that this was a 44/48 weapon consistently, as times when the 4 points of magic are resisted, would just count as a hit that isn't for max damage.  Not a huge deal.<br><br>I still stick to my opinion that this is the best cost/ratio weapon.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>D'Tox</td></tr>
